    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204880/extras/fff24618f123977751b7ec2eb520b3e7.avif?t=1705088457\" width=366 height=70 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >What is Pavephobia?</h2>Pavephobia is an action game that allows players to control the level's construction.  <br>Players can choose to encounter either a trap or an enemy at each stage of the game. <br>Collect enough money to purchase helpful tools and weapons.<br>And last but not least, boss fights.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204880/extras/2a3d21d3dc86eb4ac832a72611a2fea7.poster.avif?t=1705088457\" width=324 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204880/extras/2a3d21d3dc86eb4ac832a72611a2fea7.webm?t=1705088457\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204880/extras/2a3d21d3dc86eb4ac832a72611a2fea7.mp4?t=1705088457\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Can you tell me more?</h2>Of course. Check out these great gifs.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204880/extras/c1368e1be6552dc044cc4af12bb6336a.webp?t=1705088457\" width=500 height=62 /></span><br>Here is a selection of level elements that will await you.<br><br>A moving platform. Do you see how it moves?<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204880/extras/891dd5b110817a05ae58db058d043050.poster.avif?t=1705088457\" width=324 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204880/extras/891dd5b110817a05ae58db058d043050.webm?t=1705088457\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204880/extras/891dd5b110817a05ae58db058d043050.mp4?t=1705088457\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>A jumping pad. For jumping.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204880/extras/709d5acbb33a6845d0f4ca7ad1808b73.poster.avif?t=1705088457\" width=324 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204880/extras/709d5acbb33a6845d0f4ca7ad1808b73.webm?t=1705088457\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204880/extras/709d5acbb33a6845d0f4ca7ad1808b73.mp4?t=1705088457\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Rooms full of monsters. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204880/extras/59248ea2b87d5643f9a4f1c22bfb569a.poster.avif?t=1705088457\" width=324 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204880/extras/59248ea2b87d5643f9a4f1c22bfb569a.webm?t=1705088457\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204880/extras/59248ea2b87d5643f9a4f1c22bfb569a.mp4?t=1705088457\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>A fire trap. It's hot.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204880/extras/8286123abbd3e66fbc35ed4a865ee43d.poster.avif?t=1705088457\" width=324 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204880/extras/8286123abbd3e66fbc35ed4a865ee43d.webm?t=1705088457\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204880/extras/8286123abbd3e66fbc35ed4a865ee43d.mp4?t=1705088457\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>A spiky trap. Don't touch!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204880/extras/0c0c7eed4c6994cf08f45832b2d07d78.poster.avif?t=1705088457\" width=324 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204880/extras/0c0c7eed4c6994cf08f45832b2d07d78.webm?t=1705088457\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204880/extras/0c0c7eed4c6994cf08f45832b2d07d78.mp4?t=1705088457\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Is there more to discover?</h2>Sure there is, just look.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204880/extras/54c37433803a97963fb224e8b294b2ce.webp?t=1705088457\" width=268 height=62 /></span><br>A selection of useful gadgets awaits you. If you have enough money of course.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204880/extras/c0b3cbb8bf4cbe144dc7894f2b0925b1.poster.avif?t=1705088457\" width=324 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204880/extras/c0b3cbb8bf4cbe144dc7894f2b0925b1.webm?t=1705088457\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204880/extras/c0b3cbb8bf4cbe144dc7894f2b0925b1.mp4?t=1705088457\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Fly around like a bird and attack from above, with the jetpack. Just like a bird does...?<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204880/extras/e9b1d316e3aea265a11b36f0015a64c0.poster.avif?t=1705088457\" width=324 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204880/extras/e9b1d316e3aea265a11b36f0015a64c0.webm?t=1705088457\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204880/extras/e9b1d316e3aea265a11b36f0015a64c0.mp4?t=1705088457\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Protect yourself with a helmet and shield.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204880/extras/1d411b1ff62ff4ee176517d15738dd0f.poster.avif?t=1705088457\" width=324 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204880/extras/1d411b1ff62ff4ee176517d15738dd0f.webm?t=1705088457\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204880/extras/1d411b1ff62ff4ee176517d15738dd0f.mp4?t=1705088457\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >That sounds good. But what about weapons?</h2>Glad you ask!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204880/extras/e0900add27bf76fe2eb3c646560f9d2a.webp?t=1705088457\" width=331 height=62 /></span><br>Here is a selection of weapons in Pavephobia. Don't worry, there will be more.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204880/extras/93e99eda0a54a3b358667c1d0dab6c6b.poster.avif?t=1705088457\" width=324 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204880/extras/93e99eda0a54a3b358667c1d0dab6c6b.webm?t=1705088457\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204880/extras/93e99eda0a54a3b358667c1d0dab6c6b.mp4?t=1705088457\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The standard sword. Sharp as a...sword.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204880/extras/713f9af6fb7195cef2e2819a7da7ce2b.poster.avif?t=1705088457\" width=324 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204880/extras/713f9af6fb7195cef2e2819a7da7ce2b.webm?t=1705088457\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204880/extras/713f9af6fb7195cef2e2819a7da7ce2b.mp4?t=1705088457\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Grenades too, of course! What else?<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204880/extras/e98ab8092112db4ba7089fdc5cfa0dd3.poster.avif?t=1705088457\" width=324 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204880/extras/e98ab8092112db4ba7089fdc5cfa0dd3.webm?t=1705088457\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204880/extras/e98ab8092112db4ba7089fdc5cfa0dd3.mp4?t=1705088457\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >And now?</h2>Add it to your wishlist or buy it. <br>Or join the Steam Community Hub and meet some other Pavephobians.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204880/extras/a9f63183f37dacd57ca51b3860332241.avif?t=1705088457\" width=460 height=92 /></span><br><br>and don't forget to add it to your wishlist...<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204880/extras/ac490ceb1baaa95abd9cc349acc69f2f.webp?t=1705088457\" width=217 height=62 /></span><br>And if you're reading this, then you've scrolled down to here and looked at all the beautiful gifs that I've painstakingly cut together. Many thanks and here is your bonus gif.<br>See you in Pavephobia!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204880/extras/34b989ec49be2aaaabc34fc1061d3033.poster.avif?t=1705088457\" width=324 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204880/extras/34b989ec49be2aaaabc34fc1061d3033.webm?t=1705088457\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204880/extras/34b989ec49be2aaaabc34fc1061d3033.mp4?t=1705088457\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
